<p>It's a tale concerning <a href="/scp-603">SCP-603</a> and WAN (Broken God, Church of Maxwellism's version). The gif is created by Fantem who is awesome and helped me a lot on this.</p>
<p>Thanks for those who helped me in the forum! Special thanks to ashausesall who translated SCP-603 into Chinese or I wouldn't have wrote it in the first place.</p>
<p>(In case anyone's interested, here's the Original Chinese version of the tale that may receive an update in the future: <a href="http://scpfoundation.123ubb.com/t5241-topic">http://scpfoundation.123ubb.com/t5241-topic</a>)</p>

